Sending out "please close question" requests for overdue questions regularly
============================================================================

Have this added to your crontab:

0 12 * * * /usr/local/bin/ruby /application/script/runner -e production 'Oracle::Question.send_close_request_for_overdues'

(for a more railsy solution, we should have a look at the delayed_job plugin)

